Package etu2011.framework.annotations

Annotation Interface ModelController

@Target(TYPE) @Retention(RUNTIME) public @interface ModelController
The ModelController annotation tells the framework that the class is a controller. It is called ModelController because it is a controller that can wrap an http request parameters within itself.
